INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('932', null, null, null, '5', '931', '207', '465', '1551239673', null, null, null, '<table class=\"TableGrid2\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"128\">\r\n<p align=\"center\">Unprofitable</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"128\">\r\n<p align=\"center\">creative</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"128\">\r\n<p align=\"center\">Invited</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"128\">\r\n<p align=\"center\">market</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"128\">\r\n<p align=\"center\">Booking</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"128\">\r\n<p align=\"center\">How long</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"128\">\r\n<p>         Needs        </p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"128\">\r\n<p align=\"center\">Fired</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"128\">\r\n<p align=\"center\">Market place</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"128\">\r\n<p align=\"center\">Market share</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"128\">\r\n<p align=\"center\">for</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"128\">\r\n<p align=\"center\">Sociable</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"128\">\r\n<p align=\"center\">profitable</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"128\">\r\n<p align=\"center\">Increase</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"128\">\r\n<p align=\"center\">how</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>1.My colleague always has a lot of new ideas for the new project. He is a very <a class=\"cloze\" href=\"#mce_temp_url#\">creative</a> man</p>\r\n<p>2.Can I have a single room <a class=\"cloze\" href=\"#mce_temp_url#\">for</a> two nights?</p>\r\n<p>3.He shouted at the customer in the office so he was <a class=\"cloze\" href=\"#mce_temp_url#\">fired</a> by the company</p>\r\n<p>4.If  you adcertise your products well, you will <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">increase</span> your sales</p>\r\n<p>5.When I travel, I don’t like <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">booking</span> rooms. I often ask my sister to do this</p>\r\n<p>6. <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">How long</span> does it take to travel from the airport to the hotel by train?</p>\r\n<p>7.The Tower Hotel meets all the <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">needs </span>of modern business travelers</p>\r\n<p>8. Hanoi is an attractive <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">market</span> for consumer goods</p>\r\n<p>9. The company hope to increase its <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">market share</span> 10% this year</p>\r\n<p>10. A <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">profitable</span> market allows companies to make money.</p>', null, '57', null, null, null, null, null);
